message ${SPELL_COLOR}Enemy Territory will not download on a standard SMGL system as /tmp is only 256M \\n\
You must increase /tmp for this package to download. \\n\
Answer no to the next question, backup /tmp and issue this command \\n\
${RED}'mount -t tmpfs tmpfs -o size=512m /tmp' ${SPELL_COLOR}\\n\
Then copy your backed-up tmp back to /tmp.${DEFAULT_COLOR} &&
sleep 20 
